{
  "id": "process-stop-001",
  "version": 1,
  "title": "API が寝落ちした夜",
  "difficulty": "beginner",
  "difficultyScore": 110,
  "timeLimitMinutes": 5,
  "service": {
    "name": "やまびこ API",
    "healthUrl": "http://localhost:8080/health"
  },
  "briefing": [
    "やまびこ API は社内売上確認画面の裏側で使われている。今夜最初の現場だ。",
    "障害対応の基本の型はいつも同じ:ログを見る → yamactl status で生死を確認する → yamactl restart で直す → health で確かめる。",
    "通常は /health が 200 を返し、access.log にリクエストが流れる。障害時は app.log と yamactl status に手がかりが出る。",
    "迷ったら右の Runbook を開けばいい。"
  ],
  "startup": [
    {
      "id": "api",
      "command": "PORT=8080 node /workspace/services/yamabiko-api/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 8080
    },
    {
      "id": "fake-db",
      "command": "node /workspace/services/fake-db/server.mjs",
      "waitForPort": 15432
    }
  ],
  "topology": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "user",
        "label": "ユーザー",
        "kind": "external"
      },
      {
        "id": "api",
        "label": "やまびこ API",
        "kind": "service",
        "processId": "api"
      },
      {
        "id": "fake-db",
        "label": "疑似データベース",
        "kind": "datastore",
        "processId": "fake-db"
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "from": "user",
        "to": "api"
      },
      {
        "from": "api",
        "to": "fake-db"
      }
    ]
  },
  "triggers": [
    {
      "id": "stop-api",
      "atMs": 20000,
      "type": "process_stop",
      "params": {
        "processId": "api"
      }
    }
  ],
  "alerts": [
    {
      "id": "http-500",
      "atMs": 35000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "Health check connection refused",
      "source": "scenario"
    },
    {
      "id": "health-check-failed",
      "atMs": 50000,
      "severity": "critical",
      "message": "やまびこ API health check failed",
      "source": "monitor"
    }
  ],
  "successConditions": [
    {
      "type": "http_status",
      "url": "http://localhost:8080/health",
      "status": 200
    },
    {
      "type": "process_running",
      "processId": "api"
    }
  ],
  "runbooks": [
    {
      "id": "runbook.process",
      "title": "API プロセス停止時の初動",
      "body": "1. 左の監視画面で HTTP 5xx と SERVICE HEALTH を確認し、何が起きているか把握する\\n2. tail -n 50 /workspace/logs/app.log でプロセスが落ちた形跡がないか確認する\\n3. yamactl status api でプロセスの生死を確認する(動いているのに応答しない場合はハングを疑う)\\n4. プロセスが落ちていれば yamactl restart api で暫定復旧する\\n5. curl localhost:8080/health で復旧確認する"
    }
  ],
  "chatMessages": [
    {
      "id": "boss-restart",
      "atMs": 70000,
      "from": "上司",
      "body": "再起動すれば直る気がする。おやすみ。"
    }
  ],
  "navigationSteps": [
    {
      "id": "nav-metrics",
      "atMs": 0,
      "hint": "左の監視画面で HTTP 5xx と SERVICE HEALTH を確認する",
      "panel": "metrics"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-log",
      "atMs": 8000,
      "hint": "app.log に停止の痕跡がないか確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "tail -n 50 /workspace/logs/app.log"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-status",
      "atMs": 14000,
      "hint": "yamactl status api でサービス状態を確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "yamactl status api"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-runbook",
      "atMs": 20000,
      "hint": "右の Runbook で復旧手順を確認する",
      "panel": "runbook"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-restart",
      "atMs": 26000,
      "hint": "yamactl restart api で再起動する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "yamactl restart api"
    },
    {
      "id": "nav-health",
      "atMs": 32000,
      "hint": "curl localhost:8080/health で 200 を確認する",
      "panel": "terminal",
      "suggestedCommand": "curl localhost:8080/health"
    }
  ]
}
